Package: GeneSwitchesScorer
Title: Identifies Progression of a Sample on a Trajectory
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Moi", "Taiga Nicholas", , "mtn1n22@soton.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5609-868X"))
Description: This package identifies the progression of a sample on a trajectory by scoring the expression levels of switching genes. 
    It depends on the GeneSwitches package for gene switch identification.
